### About Me
Hi, my name is Chris LaVoy and I'm currently pursuing my bachelors in computer science at Arizona State University. I work part time as a student web/mobile developer for the university. Outside of work I pursue various hobbies and interests including 

* Game and application development
* Trying new programming languages
* Learning new languages
